                                                    <div style="margin-bottom: 1em;"><p>Alex Pothen, SM Ferdous and Fredrik Manne, <strong>Approximation algorithms in combinatorial scientific computing</strong>, Acta Numerica, 28, pp. 541-633, 2021.Â <a href="https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/acta-numerica/article/abs/approximation-algorithms-in-combinatorial-scientific-computing/8B1B0396F6DF012CFBDF52E686197DFC">https://www.cambridge.org/core</a>/journals/acta-numerica/article/abs/approximation-algorithms-in-combinatorial-scientific-computing/8B1B0396F6DF012CFBDF52E686197DFC</p></div>
