                                                    <div style="margin-bottom: 1em;"><p>Yu-Hong Yeung, Alex Pothen, Mahantesh Halappanavar and Zhenyu Huang, <strong>AMPS: An augmented matrix formulation for principal submatrix updates with application to power grids</strong>, SIAM J. Scientific Computing, 39(5) S809-827, 2017. <a href="https://www.cs.purdue.edu/homes/apothen/Papers/AMPS.pdf">https://www.cs.purdue.edu/home</a>s/apothen/Papers/AMPS.pdf</p></div>
                                                    <div style="margin-bottom: 1em;"><p>Mu Wang, Assefaw Gebremdhin and Alex Pothen, <strong>Capitalizing on live variables: Efficient Hessian Computations for Automatic Differentiation</strong>, Mathematical Programming Computation, 8(4) pp. 393-433, 2016. <br/><a href="https://www.readcube.com/articles/10.1007%2Fs12532-016-0100-3?author_access_token=_Oa2d8idQPUQ4F8LiEv5Tve4RwlQNchNByi7wbcMAY7FQZXr3zx7d9uiW0ZfFSQqHL1WXbbjlZre3uPz7ijONnQcelkgO4aYZ7D5WNxwGTKJSsRIw2sggMPhdv27n2niQ1GZzbpSFbi-oTrQLcr7Fg==">https://www.readcube.com/articles/10.1007%2Fs12532-016-0100-3?author_access_token=_Oa2d8idQPUQ4F8LiEv5Tve4RwlQNchNByi7wbcMAY7FQZXr3zx7d9uiW0ZfFSQqHL1WXbbjlZre3uPz7ijONnQcelkgO4aYZ7D5WNxwGTKJSsRIw2sggMPhdv27n2niQ1GZzbpSFbi-oTrQLcr7Fg==</a></p></div>
